These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, parkour, baseball, sailing
House: cape-cod, palace, art-deco, gothic-revival
1. the palace house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is the gothic-revival house##1
3. the art-deco house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Sport          | sailing | baseball | parkour | cricket   |
| House   | palace  | cape-cod     | art-deco   | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, almond-milk, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, rock, salsa, reggae
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of rock##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | milk    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | rock      | indie | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, analyst, bartender, nurse
4 different games are played: go, billiard, whist, monopoly
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the manager is the person playing go##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the nurse##1
5. the bartender is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Job         | manager | nurse | bartender   | analyst |
| Game   | go   | whist | monopoly | billiard         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, january, june, december
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, soy-milk, cola
1. the person drinking 7up is the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | december | january | february  | june      |
| Beverage         | 7up | cola   | soy-milk | tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, tram, skateboard
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, d&b, indie, funk
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Transport   | skateboard | tram | quad-bike | bike |
| Music-Genre    | soul       | funk | indie | d&b     |

