.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, ice-hockey, tennis
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, apple, banana, grapes
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating apple##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Sport   | tennis | ice-hockey | lacrosse | handball |
| Food           | cucumber      | banana | grapes | apple    |

