.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, photographer, security-guard, analyst
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower, sunflower, marigold
1. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
2. the analyst is on the far right##1
3. the security-guard is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
5. the photographer is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Job   | security-guard | photographer | chef | analyst  |
| Flower           | sunflower | iris | marigold       | bellflower |

