.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, pony, fish, chinchilla
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, chinese, indian, brazilian
1. the brazilian is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the brazilian is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the chinese##1
5. the australian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Pet         | fish | ferret      | pony | chinchilla |
| Nationality   | australian          | chinese | indian     | brazilian    |

