.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, r&b, techno, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, french, american, chinese
1. the chinese is on the left of the mexican##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the mexican##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
4. the french is on the left of the american##1
5. the chinese is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno       | d&b | ambient   |
| Nationality     | french | american | chinese   | mexican |

