.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, skydiving, collecting, rock-climbing
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, canadian, russian, indian
1. the australian is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the indian is on the left of the russian##1
4. the canadian is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby    | sudoku | collecting  | skydiving | rock-climbing |
| Nationality   | indian | russian | canadian          | australian    |

