.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, magic-tricks, collecting, writing
City: liverpool, prague, hannover, rome
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Hobby      | collecting | magic-tricks  | dancing | writing |
| City   | liverpool  | hannover | rome           | prague   |

