.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, romance, adventure, musical
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, camping, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | mystery | musical | adventure  |
| Hobby           | hiking | rock-climbing      | camping | gardening |

