.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, lavender, lilac, brown
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, cycling, climbing
1. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who likes apricot##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who likes lilac is the person who's sport is cycling##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Color   | lilac | lavender  | apricot | brown   |
| Sport        | cycling | rowing | climbing    | badminton |

