.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, mouse, horse
4 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, bridge, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Pet   | mouse | horse     | chinchilla | rabbit |
| Game         | billiard | mah-jongg | domino   | bridge   |

