.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, skydiving, cooking, board-games
House: wooden, palace, gothic-revival, ranch-style
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Hobby           | camping | board-games    | skydiving    | cooking |
| House   | palace      | gothic-revival | wooden | ranch-style       |

