.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, hip-hop, punk, funk
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, manager, videographer, software-developer
1. the software-developer is the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of house is the manager##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left of the videographer##1
4. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the software-developer is on the right of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop      | punk | funk | house |
| Job     | doctor | software-developer    | videographer  | manager |

