.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-18::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, snowboarding, water-polo, parkour
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, havana, fonseca, cain
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the cain-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Sport      | climbing   | parkour | snowboarding   | water-polo      |
| Cigar   | bolivar | cain      | havana | fonseca |

