.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daffodil, lily, sunflower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, classical, blues, punk
1. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of blues is the person who growslily##1
4. the fan of blues is on the left of the fan of techno##1
5. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Flower         | daffodil | lily | sunflower | poppy |
| Music-Genre   | punk     | blues    | techno      | classical   |

