.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
4 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, go, canasta
City: san-francisco, liverpool, nizza, hannover
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing canasta is the person traveling to hannover##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Game   | snooker | go | scrabble | canasta   |
| City     | nizza  | san-francisco    | liverpool       | hannover |

 